Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:10.29,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, don't call me with this name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're out here without any bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:16.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry back to St George Cathedral as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:22.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own home, and I can't stay always in inside of this old church.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking is also good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are really narrow-minded man, Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:36.14,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even find in yourself to enjoy the walk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.19,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura Stuart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:39.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,may I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:41.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are very cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:42.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:46.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just why are you speaking like a simpleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:52.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I even had a real Japanese check it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:58.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And just who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:01.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado Motoharu was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:05.61,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't take his advice on standard Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:14.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A communication talisman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.39,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of {\i1}The Book of Law{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.51,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,A magical grimoire, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:23.93,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,The author was... Edward Alexander.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:28.60,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,The original was kept in the Vatican Library in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.73,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one has been able to decipher it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:37.20,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the one who memorized the 103,000 Forbidden Grimoires hasn't been able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:42.44,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what if someone who could decipher {\i1}The Book of Law{\i0} were to appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:43.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:53.57,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is a Roman Catholic Nun named Orsola Aquinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:57.69,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be they intend to use {\i1}The Book of Law{\i0} to provoke a conflict?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:58.58,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:01.18,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,At least for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:08.97,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Book of Law{\i0} and Orsola Aquinas; both of these have been abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.49,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we discuss the details inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The second semester seems to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:55.06,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Champion Star Festival, Grand Ability Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Arts Appreciation Day, Social Learning Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.06,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.16,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Sphinx?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:07.24,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But free time is boring! I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.14,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma doesn't play with me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:14.06,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma has his own reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he stays at school because he likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.67,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you at school, Maika?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:30.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A basic of maid training is practical work experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:36.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to go to Touma's class to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.61,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The way of a maid is harsh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be hard for a woman with zero skill in housekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.72,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Touma will be a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll get him to play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.94,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do me a favour and don't repeat that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.11,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.82,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:10.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have time to become a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.18,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And neither does he.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.54,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}Sign: Be prepared! Letfs work hard for Grand Champion Star Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Champion Star Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:25.01,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge event that all the schools in Academy City participate in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:29.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The aim is to observe mutual interference between different abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:35.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,On those days, participants are authorized to use their full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:46.82,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kamijou Touma, have lost my memories due to certain circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:53.17,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't remember anything about such a large event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:08.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what should we have for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-K-K-Kamijou Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.02,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The silver-haired sister was taken away by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kidnapping! Abduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.70,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper gave me this when he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you value her life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:46.17,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,come alone to the abandoned Gloaming House Theatre outside Academy City at seven tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, just what did this guy look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been over 180 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:58.35,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,His hair was dyed red, and he had a barcode under his right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:02.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a cigarette in his mouth, and a bunch of piercings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Maika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:06.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Index and I know the offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.07,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the offender?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the motive out of twisted love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.23,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exit permits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.17,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Book of Law{\i0} has been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:35.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who can decode it, Orsola Aquinas, was also kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.12,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems that the culprit is the Amakusa sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:46.11,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they remove it form the high security Vatican Library?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:51.66,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman Catholic Church sent {\i1}The Book of Law{\i0} to a Japanese museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.71,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:08:01.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Roman Catholic Church requested the cooperation of the Church of England?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's a more pressing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:06.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't contact Kanzaki Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki is the former leader of Amakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she discovers that they're in conflict with the Roman Catholic Church...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:25.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to settle this before Kanzaki does something unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:29.62,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what methods you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:35.19,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki is a Saint, one of less than twenty in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:40.25,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't expect me to fight with Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.71,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, simply go to Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl, bring this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:57.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little gift for Orsola Aquinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Index of Forbidden Grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.66,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need the aid of a specialist, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Touma need to be involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to get involved with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.38,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are we going to the Amakusa Catholics' base?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.08,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the situation has changed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:38.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:44.14,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that "Gloaming House"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything outside of Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.04,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.83,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's an acquaintance of Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:05.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:11.83,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know if I can take this bus to get to Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no buses to Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:17.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.08,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.22,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,All transport to the outside is cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is gate over there, so if you walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:32.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking time out of your busy schedule to guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.36,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you can't take the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:42.09,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go that way, you'll get to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:46.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being such a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:52.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You just smiled and ignored everything I said, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:12.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but you seem to be sweating quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.06,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.23,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why do you want to go to Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,being hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation right now is chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our information's confused, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.84,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what happened to {\i1}The Book of Law{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:42.63,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should introduce myself, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.72,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Agnese Sanctis of the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.26,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of techniques does the Amakusa sect use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:57.70,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, we haven't been able to make a proper analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.53,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amakusa's speciality is secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:05.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amakusa don't use any spells or magical arrays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:10.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They hide all rituals and incantations in everyday actions or customs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,so even a pro magician can't make a proper identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Orsola Aquinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:34.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this kidnapping game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.67,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:45.32,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you here to help me find a missing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Find?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to hand over the sister beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:54.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:00.63,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,the sister beside you is the person we're looking for: Orsola Aquinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:04.64,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you, you can go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:11.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I have to walk all the way here in this heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.31,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thanked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:17.11,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You want me to treat you to some shaved ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:24.15,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now, even though our personalities don't match, I thought we could get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.86,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, at least until this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to care?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:36.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cure your loneliness, and nor do I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.75,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Orsola over to Agnese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, didn't you say that you were being hunted by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.32,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Orsola?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:51.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy to take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:58.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Orsola Aquinas, rather than return to the Roman Catholics, perhaps you should join us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:01.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,and enjoy a much more meaningful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:02.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Orsola!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:17.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand, bring fire, shape it into a blade, and bring forth{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:27.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better give me a proper explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:35.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who needs an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:47.36,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Book of Law{\i0} is a grimoire written in a cipher that no one in the world can decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:52.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone manages to decode it, they will gain enormous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:54.29,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that valuable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone is able to use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:04.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's said that the world dominated by the Christian religion will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just burn the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:09.22,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic books don't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.17,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,At best, you can only seal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:24.94,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to start explaining the situation, but{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:50.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, this is past the limit of simple mischief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.37,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:16:02.08,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we can be certain that Orsola Aquinas is in the hands of Amakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:07.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are roughly 50 members of Amakusa involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that they're on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,In others words, you don't know anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:18.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to track Amakusa using the traces of magic they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:23.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amakusa specializes in escaping and hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.29,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be captured so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But they can't possibly escape our perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Special movement method:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Map Pilgrimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.81,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a spell that can only be used in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:42.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, there are 47 special vortexes around Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,One can move freely between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.06,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic map.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.82,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over if they use a vortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you sitting around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:59.04,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Map Pilgrimage is ruled over by the movement of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless the stars are right, then the special movement can't be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:08.76,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Restriction of special movement only lifts just after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:11.01,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have four and a half hours until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.26,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.18,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:16.83,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:20.92,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:27.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Within this area, there's only one vortex they can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.35,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.66,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:44.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I keep telling you to check it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.29,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the sisters have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.15,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Index's tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.39,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a slug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A slug...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:32.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.11,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Amakusa had attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.66,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down, Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:05.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't how you usually react.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.71,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not usually like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember your normal{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.61,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rather annoyed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which girl do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:34.94,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady I most respect is Elizabeth the First, the Lady I most admire is St. Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:41.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the Amakusa Catholics the organization Kanzaki Kaori was serving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.11,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:49.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Amakusa are Kanzaki's comrades, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.92,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:20:00.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided to do anything to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will burn them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn them away to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.69,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I swore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:16.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if you forget everything, I won't forget a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, I live and die."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:23.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:36.39,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.19,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait, Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.29,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:56.49,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.63,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.82,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay for me to bite Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:06.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to show him my discontent with all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey wait, Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is undoubtedly real{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.64,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting Pope,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.23,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,all preparations for the Map Pilgrimage are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.18,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.08,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.04,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:53.39,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,the current form of the Amakusa-style Church of Distinct Doctrines.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We jump into the vortex with the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:31.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The result: Tatemiya Saiji has spoken an unbelievable truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Orsola...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Amakusa-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.15,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, the story begins.
